     9â†’ * Usage:
    10â†’ *   node claude-sync-cli.js init              # Initialize sync
    11â†’ *   node claude-sync-cli.js status            # Check sync status
    12â†’ *   node claude-sync-cli.js open              # Open history folder
    13â†’ *   node claude-sync-cli.js clean             # Clean sensitive data from session files
